cient ruins. I want to create something, and leave something behind that\u2019s worthwhile."), mdx("p", null, "I hope that many of these small things work. Working out well again, eating well, sleeping well. Making sure that I can study well each day, add to my portfolio or skills. Talk to someone new, maybe start something interesting. And most of all, when I recognize opportunity, to have the courage to take it."), mdx("p", null, "This is my promise to be better."), mdx("p", null, "I have high hopes for this year (yeah, right after this depressing and depressingly-long read). I know that a ton of obstacles await me, but I believe that I\u2019ll be able to overcome them. If I fail, I hope that you\u2019ll be there waiting, to talk to me and to bring me back up. And I hope to do the same for you, to hear your own triumphs and failures, and do whatever I can."), mdx("p", null, "When I see you again, I know we\u2019ll have many stories to share, but many, many more to live."), mdx("hr", null), mdx("p", null, "With Love."));
